<div id="pf506" class="pf w6 h128" data-page-no="506"><div class="pc pc506 w6 h128"><div class="t m10a x69 h2f y774 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE GOSPEL BY JOHN. </div><div class="t m5 x4b h2f y774 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">î˜‰</div><div class="t mfd3 x5 h2f y99a ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">47 </div><div class="t md06 x43 h2f ycfc ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE. </div><div class="t m1316 x5d h2f y2069 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE </div><div class="t m365 x6f he y2069 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">object of this review lesson is to present before the mind a </div><div class="t m7e2 x16 he yce7 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">comprehensive view of the lessons studied during the past quarter, </div><div class="t m605 x16 he y1c9 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and to fix more definitely some of the leading thoughts. The out-</div><div class="t m358 x16 he y1576 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">line given above is merely a suggestive one, and each student may </div><div class="t m7aa x16 he y467 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">feel at liberty to vary it as he thinks best. If a week of indepen-</div><div class="t m303 x16 he y7ed ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">dent personal study should be put upon these five chapters, and </div><div class="t m833 x16 he y859 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">then different ones should state briefly the results of their study, it </div><div class="t m5f3 x71 he y212 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">might prove to be a very profitable review. If faithful study has </div><div class="t m808 x71 he y6cf ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">been given to the lessons during the quarter, this review lesson will </div><div class="t m5f3 x16 he y15ed ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not be a taxing one. It will be found helpful to read and re-read </div><div class="t m669 x71 he y264 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the chapters several times during the week, and to make the lesson </div><div class="t mb1d x71 he y12cf ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the subject of daily meditation. </div><div class="t m404 xb h13 y666 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0